---
import EventLayout from '../../layouts/EventLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<EventLayout
  title="1st Annual Renewing Culture Conference"
  date="2025-10-04"
  location="Edmonton, AB"
  image="/images/events/2026-renewing-culture-conference-art.jpg"
  imageAlt="Adoration of the Mystic Lamb — van Eyck"
  tag="Conference"
  past={true}
>
  <p>
    The inaugural <strong>Renewing Culture Conference</strong> — the Gregory the Great Institute's
    first major public gathering. Christians from across Alberta came together for a day of
    talks, discussion, prayer, and fellowship focused on the renewal of Catholic culture in Canada.
  </p>

  <p>
    This event marked a turning point for the Institute, demonstrating that there is a deep
    hunger among Canadian Catholics for serious intellectual and cultural formation. The energy
    and connections forged at this conference directly shaped the Institute's 2026 programming.
  </p>

  <p>
    The 2nd Annual conference — <em>Bringing Back Sunday</em> — takes place October 2–3, 2026.
  </p>
</EventLayout>
